window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Previously published in the anthology <i>Dark Bites</i>, Sherrilyn Kenyon's <i>A Hard Day's Night Searcher</i> is now available as a standalone audiobook! </p> <p>As a Dark-Hunter and an immortal pirate who once intimidated the entire Spanish Main, Rafael Santiago thinks he has it made. </p> <p>Until his Squire writes a story that threatens to expose their covert world and Celena shows up to kill him for the story. </p> <p>In order to protect his Squire, he is now forced to endure Celena, who is the greatest aggravation of his life. </p> <p>Celena, for all her bluster, only wants what's best for all Dark-Hunters, but there's something about Rafael that makes her want to forsake her deepest held oath. That is if her well intentions don't kill him first. </p>"; 
